<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Basic Front Page GUI</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #eef2f7;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      background: #4a69bd;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Container */
    .container {
      width: 50%;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Form elements */
    label {
      font-weight: bold;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    input, select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px;
      margin-top: 5px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    /* Inline elements */
    .inline {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .buttons {
      margin-top: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    button {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 5px;
    }

    .submit {
      background: #2ecc71;
      color: white;
    }

    .reset {
      background: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #4a69bd;
      color: white;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>My Front Page</h1>
  <p>Basic GUI Components Demo</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <h2>User Form</h2>

  <form>

```
<!-- Textbox -->
<label>Full Name</label>
<input type="text" placeholder="Enter your name">

<!-- Email -->
<label>Email</label>
<input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email">

<!-- Password -->
<label>Password</label>
<input type="password">

<!-- Number Box -->
<label>Age</label>
<input type="number" min="1" max="100">

<!-- Dropdown -->
<label>Country</label>
<select>
  <option>Select Country</option>
  <option>India</option>
  <option>USA</option>
  <option>UK</option>
</select>

<!-- Radio Buttons -->
<label>Gender</label>
<div class="inline">
  <label><input type="radio" name="gender"> Male</label>
  <label><input type="radio" name="gender"> Female</label>
</div>

<!-- Checkbox -->
<label>Hobbies</label>
<div class="inline">
  <label><input type="checkbox"> Reading</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox"> Sports</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox"> Music</label>
</div>

<!-- Date -->
<label>Date of Birth</label>
<input type="date">

<!-- File Upload -->
<label>Upload File</label>
<input type="file">

<!-- Textarea -->
<label>Address</label>
<textarea rows="4" placeholder="Enter your address"></textarea>

<!-- Buttons -->
<div class="buttons">
  <button type="submit" class="submit">Submit</button>
  <button type="reset" class="reset">Reset</button>
</div>
```

  </form>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Basic GUI Page
</footer>

</body>
</html>
